打你有興趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但冇tg<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n轉左tg 名啦我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1076109c5e8a8edbc689e15e18a70f3b7a1695a","tid":273811,"uid":13952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T05:08:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>無拖拍加無朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nwhy so dry<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e60f400412541073ec911353385727ca56ea1fa","tid":273811,"uid":116734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T05:09:35.000Z","msg":"絲打幾歲？<br />\n<br />\n利申： 拍拖絲小女仔朋友"},{"pid":"17326d4e09245ee582cb98b50c24f3a7ce223999","tid":273811,"uid":78770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T05:09:52.000Z","msg":"絲打我同你情況一樣<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b314b7df10bca2932657933e3c8fa5c6266fecb1","tid":273811,"uid":13952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T05:10:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>女朋友小學識到而家 朋友圈子差唔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁sweet 由小學已經識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唉我依家去男朋友同波友既聚會仲多過我同自己班frd 食飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 無朋友好慘<br />\n其實我又唔係無 但男仔朋友比較多 拍左拖就自動同佢地疏遠晒 搞到得返少數女仔朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f64b492649f3aa11d06cd664787bcad82ed6f0b","tid":273811,"uid":53358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T05:10:32.000Z","msg":"其實男朋友同朋友兩邊都要平衡下，有男友以外既社交都好緊要，唔好一拍拖就好似失左蹤咁朋友都唔揾，如果一個唔好彩唔夾要分手，到