f\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 無朋友好慘<br />\n其實我又唔係無 但男仔朋友比較多 拍左拖就自動同佢地疏遠晒 搞到得返少數女仔朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有自己空間好重要 唔使為左另一半去疏遠自己既朋友<br />\n最重要係雙方都比到信心大家</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n費是啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 調返轉頭諗我都會唔鐘意佢同其他女仔frd 玩得咁埋 話我小氣都係咁講<br />\n之前已經為左依樣嘈過幾次 所以自動疏遠佢地就完左件事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"599da45881c05c7f42c3fb371bbf3f1d95c8662a","tid":273811,"uid":13952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T06:50:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同絲打差唔多，冇朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲要中學d朋友好中意去d有好多男仔既gathering<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我有男朋友又點會去得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n只此疏遠了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唉我都係 陣間男朋友知道左又有排嘈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n疏下疏下就無乜朋友了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e1abaef069ecd3f8da87b9acc1c4655b571c03b","tid":273811,"uid":13952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T06:51:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我自己本身身活圈子好窄<br />\n個人又好摺 成日都無乜朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n同我一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 依家已經變到一個人行街一個人食飯都無問題了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd8b3ff53df3b2cc69bb470752851b76ed994178","tid":273811,"uid":13952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T06:51:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>開返個毒絲群有冇得諗？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj